Ryan’s Rockin’ Layered Salad

Ingredients:
1 Cup prepared low fat Ranch salad dressing
1 Cup prepared salsa 
1 (10-ounce) package DOLE Hearts of Romaine Mix
1(10-ounce) package DOLE Shredded Carrots
1(15-ounce) can black beans, drained and rinsed 
1(15-ounce)can whole kernel corn, drained
1 Small DOLE Premium Red Onion, diced
1 Cup finely shredded reduced fat Cheddar cheese 

1. Combine Ranch dressing and salsa; set aside
2. In a large bowl, layer the romaine mix, carrots, black beans, corn, 
red union, and cheese. Pour the dressing/salsa mixture on top; 
chill for 45-60 min in refrigerator 
3.    When ready serve with crushed tortilla chips
